It's important to remember that every individual has the right to seek safety and better opportunities, regardless of their origin. Closing borders to all immigrants, including those seeking refuge, doesn't solve problems; it exacerbates them. Constructive dialogue and fair policies that address the root causes of migration are essential. Let's focus on creating inclusive solutions that respect human rights and foster global cooperation.
